\p YaŇč do aŇček PiŇčkop da don saŇčbek saŇčbek kalug…® k…®nda ag…®t. UŇčun yaŇč. Am…®n morap Yesu Kristo nandaŇč gadaŇč …®mni uŇčun PiŇčkop da dab…®lon am…®n k…®leg…®si ani do yaŇč tebantok aŇčyomgut. (Mt 26.28; Mk 14.24; Lk¬†22.20; Ro 11.27; 1Ko 11.25; 2Ko 3.6; Ibr 7.22, 8.6-13, 9.15, 10.16, 29, 12.24, 13.20) SaŇčbek SaŇčbek K…®nam ‚Äď PiŇčkop da Israel am…®n yoy…®Ňčban k…®ndap baŇč k…®nam k…®r…®Ňč k…®nda wasawit. AŇček gol baŇč kwenikon w…®tj…®wit. UŇčun k…®namgwan PiŇčkop da saŇčbek saŇčbek ag…®t dakon telag…® yo d…® yopgwit. T…®p bamot PiŇčkop da gen teban 10 kab…® mandag…®t gat, ae Aron dakon win gat, ae kwoba mana s…®m…®lbi gat uŇčungwan tawit. UŇčun k…®nam da kwenon aŇčelo bamor…® serabim yaŇč yoŇč uŇčun dakon wupm…® wasawit. Israel am…®n dukwan dukwan k…®k do awit uŇčun k…®nam k…®r…®Ňč simon da guram…®gek k…®Ňč k…®Ňč awit. (Ibr 9.4; PA 11.19; Kap 78.61, 132.6-8)  
